<paragraph blockId="10.[189,1398,1962,2024]" pageId="10" pageNumber="173">
This species was originally described from 
<collectingCountry box="[705,809,1962,1988]" name="Thailand" pageId="10" pageNumber="173">Thailand</collectingCountry>
based on 
<specimenCount box="[931,1055,1962,1988]" pageId="10" pageNumber="173" type="male">three male</specimenCount>
specimens. In this paper, we newly record this species in 
<collectingCountry box="[523,593,1998,2024]" name="China" pageId="10" pageNumber="173">China</collectingCountry>
and describe its female for the first time.
</paragraph>
